# Project Memory ‚Äî InstaGold (Gold)

## App Identity
- App name: **InstaGold** (package: com.ibrahym.goldfamily)
- Platform: **Android only** ‚Äî ignore iOS for UI, testing, screenshots
- APK outputs at repo root: **`InstaGold-dev.apk`** (dev flavor, test ads, label ‚ÄúInstaGold Dev‚Äù) via `./scripts/build-dev-apk.sh`; **`InstaGold.apk`** (prod) via `./scripts/build-and-upload.sh` or `flutter build apk --flavor prod`
- Play Store bundle: `./scripts/build-play-aab.sh` ‚Üí `app-prod-release.aab`
- Firebase project: goldcalculate

## Architecture
- Monorepo: `scraper-service/` (price scraping), `main-backend/` (API), `flutter-app/` (mobile UI)
- Mobile mode: local SQLite + direct scraping ‚Äî no backend servers needed on device
- Web mode: talks to main-backend HTTP APIs
- No CI/CD pipelines

## UI Design Decisions
- Muted warm-gold ColorScheme: light `#9E8A4F`, dark `#BFA764`, light surface cream `#FAF8F3`
- Cards: 0.5px outlines, 14px radius, zero elevation, white in light mode
- Price cards: gold gradient rounded rectangles, drag-and-drop reorderable
- Home layout: 21K full-width hero ‚Üí 24K+18K row ‚Üí 14K full-width ‚Üí Pound+Ounce row
- Gap card: full-width tinted box (green/red), EGP gap value large and centred, tappable for explanation popup showing calculation breakdown
- Ounce card: shiny gold gradient `[#E0C45C, #CCAE3A, #AA9028]`
- Asset cards: icon in gold circle (ClipOval for PNGs), title, karat/weight/date subtitle, Purchase/Current/Profit rows with %
- Bottom nav: outlined/filled icon states with thin top divider
- No custom ClipPath shapes ‚Äî standard rounded containers only

## Code Patterns
- Dialog builders: always use builder context (`ctx`) for AppStrings, Theme, Navigator ‚Äî never State's `context`
- Member: name field only, no relation field. API `addMember`/`updateMember` have optional relation param
- Localization: `AppStrings.t(context, 'key')` ‚Äî Arabic and English
- Colors: `withValues(alpha: ...)` not deprecated `withOpacity`
- Theme variant: `kUiDesignVariant` in `ui_design_variant.dart` ‚Äî set to `classic` to rollback

